actions.text: Referred to House Committee on House Administration.
Reported to House from the Committee on House Administration, H. Rept. 93-577.

official_title: Resolution providing for printing of additional copies of oversight hearings entitled "Vocational Rehabilitation Services".

summary.text: Provides that there shall be printed for the use of the Committee on Education and Labor, House of Representatives, two thousand additional copies of the Oversight Hearings before the Select Subcommittee on Education on August 3, 1973, entitled "Vocational Rehabilitation Services".
